Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as flowing water has no\Nform, and the breeze is invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Deductions take all shapes and styles\Nin each and every case to be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we must all\Nchange out way of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What should be on, isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees through to the one & only truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:02:00.77,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(351.371,335.429)}A MYSTERIOUS GUNSHOT\NECHO IN THE DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So many handsome actors star in\Nthose Monday night mystery shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited, I wonder what\Nkind of stories we'll get to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because our client's the president\Nof some company produces movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid insisted on tagging along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I already told you but my job\Nis to protect the client's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was injured when she was\Nattacked 3 days ago, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is being the president of a finance\Ncompany such a dangerous job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've heard she can be pretty vicious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means she's got\Na lot of enemies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kogoro Mouri,\NI'm a private investigator...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a 7'o clock appointment\Nto see Ms. Etsuko Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're expected. I'll unlock\Nthe gate now. Please come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Conan? We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have some coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm terribly sorry about this,\NMs. Furukawa is usually punctual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:20.08,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(336.272,348)}Azusa Machida\NFurukawa Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't be bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's alright with you, while we're waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we watch the television?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That TV's been on\Nthe brink since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing shows on the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, you have some\Nnerve asking like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the window on the far left on the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd floor facing the street was open...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That room belongs to\Nthe owner of this place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Katsue Furukawa, president\Nof the Furukawa Finance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for asking, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohji Furukawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her son
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That window is always open at\Nthis time of day to air out the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:05.39,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.046,324.571)}Kohji Furukawa\NEldest Son Unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Azusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that detective my\Nsister hired, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I pity you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just going to use you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Use me? You say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's her now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's me, Etsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:31.22,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.676,325.143)}Etsuko Furukawa\NEldest Daughter TV Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm late. Hurry & let me in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, right away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mouri, I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some last minute\Nbusinesss to take care of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi sis, long time no see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't mom ban you from this\Nhouse the last time you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw shut up, this is MY house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the way, what's with that watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You said digitals were cheap stuff and\Nyou wouldn't be caught dead with one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to pawn that Swiss watch you\Nwere so proud of to pay for your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kohji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you're here to get mom to\Npay off your debts again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you sis, hiring a\Nprivate detective to butter mom up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Things seem pretty messy around here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Etsuko's company is on\Nthe verge of bankruptcy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems Mr. Kohji has\Na lot of gambling debts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And some mobsters after him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But their mother Katsue\Nhas a lot of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Mrs. Furukawa\Nnever lends money to those
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels cannot repay her,\Nregardless if they're her children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past though, she did lend Kohji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of money but it got out of and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So she finally banned\Nhim from the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa, what is wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you telling them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alseep in her room, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of doing everything\Nmy sister tells you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go out with me sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask, I can get mom to forget\Nabout all the money you owe her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohji! If you have nothing better to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go out and\Nbuy something to give mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go Azusa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, about Azusa's debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I heard she made a\Nstain on mom's Persian rug today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for that, she's not\Ngetting a bonus this year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And since that wasn't enough, mom\Nmade her write an IOU for the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happened several times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these days, I'm sure\Nshe's going to blow up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess I'll go and buy mom\Na little something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate taking sis's advice though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this family...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She usually gets up right away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she took some of the sleeping\Npills the doctor prescribed and fell asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it certainly is hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mouri, something's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from mom's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear a weird\Nsound from mom's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a gunshot in mom's room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked. Do you have a spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The key was a special order\Nitem and mom has the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other choice, we've\Ngot to break the door down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark you can't see a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the light swtich?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,On the wall to your left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,M, mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,B, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a murder! We have to\Npreserve the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran, call the police
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been shot in the forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She died instantaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There're no signs of a struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Footprints lead to the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer must've used that ladder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the position of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you! How many times do\NI have to repeat myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim is Katsue Furukawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,64 years old, president\Nof a finance company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The footprints around the body match\Nthose we found around the ladder outside
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim was attacked just\N3 days earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the same assailant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh officer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone you didn't know\Ncame in through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you run for the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!\NI told you to stay out of this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Conan's right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the body was near the window
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can assume the victim noticed the\Nintruder and approached the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means the intruder was\Nprobably someone the victim knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's question everyone who was\Nin the house when the murder occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,About when you discovered the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Etsuko Furukawa and\NMs. Azusa Machida, you two
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,went to the victim's room\Non the 2nd floor to wake her up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And heard the gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Mouri and Mr. Kohji Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Broke the door down and\Nthen discovered the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you heard the gunshot, did you\Nnotice anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very certain it was when\NMiss Etsuko bent down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To pick up the handkerchief she dropped,\Nthat's when we heard the gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about after the gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious she was killed by the same\Nperson who attacked her 3 days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out an all points bulletin, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's already been\Ntaken care of. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the position of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance\Nshe knew her killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we suspects?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I left this morning and\Nhaven't been in mom's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa Machida...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the victim\Ntreated you quite badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,According to your neighbor, you\Nwere complaining about it this evening
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, "I'll get back at her for this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh, you finally lost your temper, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong. I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, I did say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I spilled some tea in the\Nmadam's room this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wiped everything that got wet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The clock, the remote control\Nfor the television, even the rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But madam insisted I stained the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said she wasn't going\Nto give me a bonus this year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then on top of that, she made me\Nwrite an IOU...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I said what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But like I said before,\Nwhen the gunshot went off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was outside the door with Ms. Etsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you two have an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Furukawa, where were you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question, Kohji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as your sister and Azusa\Nwent upstairs, you left the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After the gunshot, you took some time\Nbefore joining us upstairs didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, hold on just one minute
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I was going to go buy mom a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And just as I was going out the gate,\NI heard a strange sound so I rushed back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you have no alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Th, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just talk\Nabout this a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things stand now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohji does seem the most suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But something just doesn't seem right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, there you are kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to help\Nthat famous detective again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to ask you if\Nthere was a cassette radio
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something with a timer in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, if you set the timer, you\Ncan pre-set the gunshot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we didn't\Nfind anything like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV's an old model and it\Ndoesn't have a timer either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Tome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good hunting, little detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so sure there was a\Ntrick behind to that gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A blue-white light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before the gunshot, I\Nhappened to look up at mom's room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And her room was lit up with a blue-white\Nlight but it got dark right after that again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to believe me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A blue-white light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Tome just told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why that thing was there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart to pick up on that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That struck me as strange too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've got all the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is the killer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, where's this solid\Nproof you were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, you know who the killer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?! Oh, I know that look!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes Inspector Megure,\NI've figured everything out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have everyone come\Nhere to this room please
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all Inspector Megure,\Njudging from the position of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've deducted the victim\Nknew the killer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we broke the door down and\Nentered the room, the lights were all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then how did the\Nvictim see the killer's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Furukawa was killed earlier in the\Nday, while there was still sunlight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,B, but what about the\Ngunshot we all heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That gunshot was staged by\Nthe killer to be used as an alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer took the remote\Ncontrol for the television
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And switched it on\Nlater to play the television
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean the killer\Nhad to have prior knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the exact time the gunshot\Nwould be heard on television?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, there's only one person here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would know the exact time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A gunshot would be\Nheard on the television...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The gunshot was heard at about 7:30.\N7:29 and 32 seconds to be exact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the exact time a gun is shot in a show\NMs. Furukawa's company produces
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Etsuko Furukawa,\Nyou are the murderer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime probably took place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Furukawa climbed\Nin through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother sees her and\Ngoes to the window
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And is shot by a gun with a silencer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Furukawa then changed her\Nclothes and came to meet with us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting as if nothing had happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then calculating the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She took Azusa,\Nwho would act as her witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Upstairs and deliberately\Ndropped her handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then pretends to pick it up as\Nshe presses the remote control button!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I made any mistakes anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the blue-white light Kohji was\Ntalking about was from the television...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If even a second was off from the timing\Nof switching the remote control on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Other noises would have been heard\Nand the trick wouldn't have worked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you wore a digital\Nwatch today, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was also you who broke\Nthe TV in living room, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When the gunshot was heard\Nupstairs, it would've been suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the same sound came from the\Ntelevision downstairs, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,C, can you prove any of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof I did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When the body was found,\Nyou pretended to cry and crouched down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When no one was looking, you took the\Nremote control out. Then slid it on the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And returned it\Nunder the table, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you put a little too\Nmuch strength into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it was supposed to look\Nlike it fell from the table
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it slid under the legs instead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fingerprints were\Non that remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I go in and out of this\Nroom practically every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But earlier you said you left the room\Nthis morning and never returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about today. But I was\Nin here yesterday and the day before too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Azusa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with the remote\Ncontrol when you spilled the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, the tea spilled on it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wiped it clean....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you forgot to wipe it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not! I wiped it absolutely clean!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh brother, this argument\Nis getting us nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tome! Please explain to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We found two sets of fingerprints\Non the remote control found on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One! The left hand print\Nof Ms. Etsuko Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the thumb to\Nbaby finger and palm print
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Second! The left hand print\Nof Ms. Azusa Machida
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the thumb to\Nbaby finger and palm print
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUR prints are on it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B, but I....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all, Mr. Tome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that settles it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what do you mean by that ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa didn't forget to\Nwipe the remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,B, but just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had forgotten\Nto wipe the remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,something else had to be on it....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsue Furukawa's fingerprints,\Nit was her room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,& since she's always handling\Nthe remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,her prints should have been on it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,.....It was all her fault....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...She knew\NI was having financial problems
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but she wouldn't lend me a single cent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet she'd pay off\Nall of Kohji's gambling debts....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always that way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always Kohji this, Kohji that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,she pampered him because\Nshe gave birth to him in her later years....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohji was everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Furukawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that\NI don't understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I do, but
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,....think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just committed a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've killed your own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want you to think deeply\Nabout what you did!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There, that should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it was nothing....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not look it\Nbut Mr. Takagi's a video freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's goes to rent videos every night,\Nhe's addicted,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunshots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,L, look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a case to solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody tell him it's already over!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y, you've.....\NYou've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to bathe\Nwith Conan, no way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's come over Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she suspects who I really am?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Genta, what's wrong?
